<br>
This is not a bug, it's there to be nice to the players.  You've lost your buffs but you didn't die while zoning.  <br>
<br>
It's just that the game doesn't know the difference between &quot;actively losing hitpoints while zoning&quot; and &quot;zoning with less hitpoints than I have buffs for&quot;.<br>
<br>
It's somewhat of a kludge but it's actually to your benefit for it being there.  <br>
<br>
-- Hika<br>
